{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-markdown-js","path":"/components/ez-link","webpackCompilationHash":"356c1bd9f0f7a983bfed","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Links are used to embed navigation paths to related content from within a page. Typically links will be used to trigger navigation to other pages in an application.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"best-practices\"><a href=\"#best-practices\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Best Practices</h2>\n<p>Link should:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Clearly indicate the destination of the navigation using text or images with assistive text.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Links should not:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Be used for embedding actions or submitting data. Consider <a href=\"/recipe/components/ez-button\">buttons</a> for this usage.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"examples\"><a href=\"#examples\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Examples</h2>\n<h3 id=\"basic-link\"><a href=\"#basic-link\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Basic link</h3>\n<p>Used for either stand-alone navigational actions or links within larger spans of text. Use the <code>href</code> prop to provide the destination url for the link.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">&#x3C;EzLink href=\"/orders\">View Orders&#x3C;/EzLink>\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"link-component\"><a href=\"#link-component\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Link component</h3>\n<p>Normally links render an <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a\">anchor element</a>, but in order to support client-side routing implementations, you can provide a Link component, such as <a href=\"https://reacttraining.com/react-router/web/api/Link\">react-router's link component</a>, to render via the optional <code>as</code> property. EzLink will forward its props to the provided component.</p>\n<p>When using the <code>as</code> prop, you must use the <code>to</code> prop in place of <code>href</code> to provide the destination url for the link.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">() => {\n  const {Link, BrowserRouter: Router, Route} = require('react-router-dom');\n  return (\n    &#x3C;Router>\n      &#x3C;EzLayout layout=\"basic\">\n        &#x3C;EzLink to=\"/orders\" as={Link}>\n          View Orders\n        &#x3C;/EzLink>\n        &#x3C;EzLink to=\"/accounts\" as={Link}>\n          View Accounts\n        &#x3C;/EzLink>\n      &#x3C;/EzLayout>\n      &#x3C;Route exact path=\"/orders\" component={() => 'Orders'} />\n      &#x3C;Route exact path=\"/accounts\" component={() => 'Accounts'} />\n    &#x3C;/Router>\n  );\n};\n</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"related-components\"><a href=\"#related-components\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Related components</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/recipe/components/ez-button\">Button</a></li>\n</ul>","htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Links are used to embed navigation paths to related content from within a page. Typically links will be used to trigger navigation to other pages in an application."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"hr","properties":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"best-practices"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#best-practices","ariaHidden":true,"className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 